{"html": [{"t": "<div><br><div class=\"p\">AUTORIZA EMISOR ELECTR&#xD3;NICO</div></div>", "i": 9290487}, {"t": "<div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Extracto de resoluci&#xF3;n exenta del Servicio de Impuestos Internos N&#xBA; 90, del 16 de agosto de 2012, que autoriza a contribuyentes como emisores electr&#xF3;nicos.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Se autoriza como emisor de documentos tributarios electr&#xF3;nicos a contribuyentes RUT 76.956.730-5, RUT 76.191.059-0, RUT 76.064.646-6, RUT 78.313.670-8, RUT 77.422.290-1, RUT 7.352.580-2, RUT 77.072.410-4, RUT 76.172.384-7, RUT 76.066.940-7, RUT 86.820.700-0, RUT 76.086.318-1, RUT 76.192.617-9, RUT 76.188.197-3, RUT 96.512.650-3, RUT 84.519.200-6, RUT 76.364.430-8, RUT 78.494.020-9, RUT 76.205.713-1, RUT 76.790.520-3, RUT 76.536.600-3, RUT 76.216.329-2, RUT 76.661.920-7, RUT 96.651.680-1, RUT 76.057.769-3, RUT 76.019.255-4, RUT 76.167.920-1, RUT 76.190.713-1, RUT 96.897.630-3, RUT 78.209.990-6, RUT 81.847.600-0, RUT 76.902.190-6, RUT 76.125.585-1, RUT 76.197.747-4, RUT 99.515.040-9, RUT 76.157.666-6, RUT 79.803.210-0, RUT 76.119.015-6, RUT 99.556.630-3, RUT 76.208.844-4, RUT 76.067.582-2, RUT 99.581.680-6, RUT 76.081.053-3, RUT 79.861.930-6, RUT 77.077.860-3, RUT 76.088.321-2, RUT 96.997.470-3, RUT 76.658.840-9, RUT 78.594.740-1, RUT 99.579.570-1, RUT 15.816.123-0, RUT 79.787.560-0, RUT 91.650.000-9, RUT 76.085.535-9, RUT 79.570.530-9, RUT 96.847.320-4, RUT 76.048.238-2, RUT 5.048.780-6, RUT 52.001.581-7, RUT 96.910.610-8, RUT 76.098.523-6, RUT 76.179.256-3, RUT 76.214.946-K, RUT 76.087.083-8, RUT 76.171.987-4, RUT 96.686.080-4, RUT 76.008.959-1, RUT 76.070.437-7, RUT 76.117.591-2, RUT 96.660.680-0, RUT 2.031.820-1, RUT 76.118.947-6, RUT 76.204.735-7, RUT 76.192.781-7, RUT 76.207.356-0, RUT 76.895.070-9, RUT 76.241.480-5, RUT 76.174.954-4, RUT 10.462.821-4, RUT 78.101.430-3, RUT 76.504.180-5, RUT 77.669.700-1, RUT 77.613.470-8, RUT 76.138.277-2, RUT 76.000.761-7, RUT 89.962.800-4, RUT 76.104.983-6, RUT 77.32